    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "（次の授業は視聴覚室やんな）\n（うちの教室からやと意外と遠いんよな～）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Next class is in the audio-visual room）\n（It's surprisingly far from my classroom~）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、瑠依ちゃんや。どこ行くんやろ）\n（ふふ。ちょっとからかったろ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ah‚ it's Rui-chan. She's going somewhere）\n（Hehe. Let's tease her a little）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7066.6666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.4666667938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ごきげんよう、瑠依先輩",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good day‚ Rui-senpai",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4666681289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.400000445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ご、ごきげんよう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? G-Good day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.400000445,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8299.998664899998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.800000445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "先輩、制服にチョークの粉が付いてますよ\nうちが払ってあげますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Senpai‚ there's chalk dust on your uniform\nI'll dust you off",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.800000445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.4333337783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。じゃなくて、なんで急に敬語なの？\n私、優に何かしたかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. That's not‚ why are you suddenly using honorific language?\nDid I do something to Yu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333337783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.7999976475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "別に怒ってるんとちゃいます。学校では上下関係を\nちゃーんとせなあかんやないですか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not angry. At school‚ shouldn't\nwe maintain a hierarchicalー relationship~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7999976475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.5333309809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "（ふふ、瑠依ちゃんってばきょとんとしてはる）\n（そんなお顔も可愛らしいわ～）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Fufu‚ Rui-chan looks confused）\n（That face is cute‚ too~）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5333309809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.6999976475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほど、一理あるわね。それじゃあ、\n私も先輩として、『上下関係』をしっかりするべきね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……I see‚ that makes sense. Well then‚\nAs a senpai‚ I should also be careful about 'hierarchical relationship'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6999976475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.3666643142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、しっかりせな……って、え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right-right‚ you have to be careful… eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3666643142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.266659228
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "こほん……優、昼休みにランニングに行くわよ\nもし来なかったら、後で二倍走ってもらうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahem…… Yu‚ let's go for a run during lunchtime\nIf you don't come‚ you'll have to run twice as far later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.266659228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.3999925613
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "え……瑠依ちゃん？　それ、誰のマネ……？\nぼんやり分かりそうな気もするんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… Rui-chan? Who are you imitating…?\nI have a vague feeling that I know it……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3999925613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.7333258946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "あと、先輩にパンケーキを買って来なさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ you have to treat your senpai to pancakes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7333258946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.0333258946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして莉央さんっ！？\nというか、莉央さんでもそないなこと言わへんって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be Rio-san!?\nIn fact‚ even Rio-san wouldn't say something like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.0333258946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.7999940872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "何をぼさっとしてるの。返事は『はい』でしょ\nそれとも、先輩にヤキを入れられたいのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you spacing out for? The answer is 'yes'‚ right?\nOr‚ maybe you want to be scolded by your senpai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7999940872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.6999940872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、それ意味分かって言ってる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ do you understand what that means?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6999940872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.9333274205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "なんかこう……きっと凄いことをするのよね\nこの前観たドラマで言っていた気がするわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something like that… I'm sure they'll do something amazing\nI think I heard it in a drama I saw a while ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9333274205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.3666607539
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんの言葉やなくて、何よりやけど……\n先輩としての接し方って、そういうんちゃうと思うで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not Rio-san's words‚ I think it's a relief that……\nI don't think‚ senpai should treat others like that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3666607539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.1999976476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "また口答えを……！　表に出なさい。あなたの顔色を\n『Blue sky summer』にしてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talking back again…! Come outside. I'll make your face\nlook like 'Blue Sky Summer'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1999976476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.6999976476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "意味分からんし、絶対怒られるって！\nうちが悪かったから、元の瑠依ちゃんに戻ってー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn't make sense‚ definitely get in trouble!\nI was bad‚ get back to the original Rui-chanー!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6999976476,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}